1. `animate-pulse` on the status dot has a reduced-motion media query in the CSS (Tailwind provides this by default)
2. `animate-spin` on the progress spinner has a reduced-motion media query (Tailwind provides this by default)
3. No motion animations use non-composited properties that could cause layout thrashing under reduced motion

